{
  "logNo": "223105349339",
  "title": "남성역한의원 소아청소년들이 한의원을 찾는 이유는",
  "addDate": "2023. 5. 18.",
  "categoryNo": "9",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=223105349339",
  "html_size": 214566,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6beaa9f0-9434-4362-a3a5-1fc763c02324\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2590dece-4420-4ea7-8770-7b22c16b2ecd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-08474718-0ac3-4604-a6cb-7be450ca241b\">안녕하세요. 남성역 이수한의원입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f6d78d11-17dc-4d06-8ba2-c753067d1ed3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ca1327c6-b664-4969-a27d-5bc8577c5ff8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b181c893-f55e-41c8-8ae1-0831e18b633c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7615d1b8-aa55-4226-a7d5-ac39c11683e0\">간혹 어린이, 소아청소년들은 한의원에 가서 치료받을 일이 없다고 생각하는 분들이 있으시더라고요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-597230a0-d27e-48ef-b2a5-6f67ed4c5ef9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-320eebdd-6030-49e7-bcc0-76b66b70c28b\">소아 보약이나 처방받으러 가지 따로 치료받으러 갈 일이 있냐고 물어보시죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bb9e654b-a19f-472d-8b59-0ce2ccff3e22\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a2c2e07d-69db-4cf4-b633-441e5c8aa52f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8525e0e9-dbfd-4e87-84f7-e8837e6de8ef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b989e8ac-8620-49b1-9b05-0bcec832cc43\">감기에 잘 걸리거나 먹는 게 부실해서 허약한 애들 한의원에서 처방해 준 보약을 복용하고 건강해지는 건 다들 잘 알고 계신데, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b6f2eb2-ee83-4b27-a3b2-07afa5d1e8b0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2e90b8b3-b73d-4d8c-8dda-895f228de1e4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d9a63977-4b78-4ca7-95eb-39279cbc58f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29a56879-f733-4962-858b-0d487f5e694f\">감기 걸렸을 때 한의원에서 치료받는 건 모르는 분도 많아요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fa044b03-acc4-4fcd-acdc-81bf105d2798\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-28dde004-88bc-4d09-808b-256e97cc9505\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-200428fb-bae9-4d3f-b5bd-9413d5b727df\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-200428fb-bae9-4d3f-b5bd-9413d5b727df\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA4MTlfNTUg/MDAxNTY2MTgwNTg1MzMy.T6Tq8nlX7xhAHQ5eVU5QEbnniKCW56ddgVD5ThsdCvEg.w2WvvLMgmO-QQTC8jPd7saB8H-fby-mDu9Mm5ao-KVMg.PNG.az3949/20190819095404.png?type=w2\", \"originalWidth\" : \"743\", \"originalHeight\" : \"512\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAxOTA4MTlfNTUg/MDAxNTY2MTgwNTg1MzMy.T6Tq8nlX7xhAHQ5eVU5QEbnniKCW56ddgVD5ThsdCvEg.w2WvvLMgmO-QQTC8jPd7saB8H-fby-mDu9Mm5ao-KVMg.PNG.az3949/20190819095404.png?type=w2\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cc7e1487-b6ae-406b-a063-86ae749d215c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-df05bd04-757b-4e58-8a8c-3ac34c575bef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b8edc98d-233a-4ae5-bf32-a4c701d205cf\">남성역 이수한의원에서는 간단하게 복용할 수 있고, 건강보험도 적용되는 &quot;보험한약&quot;들이 준비되어 있어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6746a9a0-d394-4220-9266-0d70032b8c17\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0fe455c5-5012-4417-9986-a2fe2f026509\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e9bc1802-1c86-437a-8504-172ce8974619\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e9bc1802-1c86-437a-8504-172ce8974619\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e4a095117aa0e20c.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"505\", \"originalHeight\" : \"432\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e4a095117aa0e20c.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e4a095117aa0e20c.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"427\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00ecd93e-a213-4b1b-8783-5bfe6163d34a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6601828b-bd7b-42c1-9c3f-a54867047c14\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b1ea9cc6-77bf-4cb2-a683-5996aeb70aa9\">건강보험은 안되지만, 저렴하고 간편하게 복용하는 효과 좋은 한약도 준비되어 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-364082ec-ab02-489d-a6aa-05645c63ce2b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-59c6c443-01f1-4d47-a1de-2deb23083d9d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-de7375b8-1a74-441b-b7e8-b8540c9f1bd4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-de7375b8-1a74-441b-b7e8-b8540c9f1bd4\", \"src\" : \"https://modo-phinf.pstatic.net/20200313_140/1584079731157f2q6z_JPEG/mosaHjV2Ij.jpeg?type=w720\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2900\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2900\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://modo-phinf.pstatic.net/20200313_140/1584079731157f2q6z_JPEG/mosaHjV2Ij.jpeg?type=w720\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9718d890-c54d-4320-9b85-c0c9b459f0d0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-be6e4726-f669-45ec-b6a3-a39ccf99535e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-170cc939-7316-4b39-96a9-ee7a46a11a22\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a278c32-ca75-44fe-a16f-6033b58cef8e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ee5daa6f-7af9-41d6-bb17-fa1b6ef8b575\">비내시경으로 콧속 점막 상태도 확인해서 더 정확한 진단을 한 후 항생제나 소염제가 아닌 간편한 한약을 처방하여 치료를 진행합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9e3daea1-435d-4fa0-885f-f268bf8f0b8c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-141d2be0-57e1-4b4c-8379-83f0106b111e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f4f8e055-ae0f-4b54-ae51-87736ec89880\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f4f8e055-ae0f-4b54-ae51-87736ec89880\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/13e3a251ad203ed7.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1312\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/13e3a251ad203ed7.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/13e3a251ad203ed7.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"656\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d8fd1348-b34e-4fdc-8b66-a698dddec65b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-31e6cd9f-b523-485b-9897-c3b7978a9a01\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-37c54ac5-c18e-4841-a072-c9950b6e11c2\">저희 한의원에는 감기 외에도 발목, 무릎, 어깨가 아파서 치료받으러 소아청소년들이 종종 내원합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6a7b72c0-7599-40aa-a70b-04053a97d67f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-39a625b3-635e-46e8-a9e6-4bacb3899a99\">인근 중학교, 초등학교 운동부 애들이 운동하다 다치거나 아프면 와서 침 치료받고 갑니다. 한 명이 와서 치료받아보고 잘 좋아지는 경험을 하고 나면 운동부 애들 전체가 와서 치료받아요. 애들끼리 서로서로 어디 가서 치료받으라고 정보를 주고받나 봅니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d9ab1be-9ba0-4823-af27-d16e35cb441b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-23c12e9b-0d01-4b5b-af8b-02a84f8055c0\">감독님 또는 코치님이 와서 치료받아보고는 좋아서 운동부원들에게 추천을 해주기도 하고요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6bf9bfd0-772a-46b1-94de-80237a2cc93d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-177f5b1c-c335-4a8d-ae2f-b3663c9c2805\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c0a2165-195f-45d9-8bb0-f0a1f2ec4661\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-5c0a2165-195f-45d9-8bb0-f0a1f2ec4661\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2abee4eaa47781d8.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1312\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2abee4eaa47781d8.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2abee4eaa47781d8.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"656\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4f46073e-7d17-499f-8fa2-609a68346f4e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f171dc75-b6aa-46c5-b26a-dff960466113\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-94aab0b3-47f0-439a-8ec9-204f43af0bcc\">공부 열심히 하는 청소년들이 어깨허리가 아파서 치료받는 경우도 많아요. 요새 애들 앉아있는 시간이 엄청 길잖아요. 가방도 무겁고.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63c06027-386d-4bf8-b479-60c316aec5c9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7bd5ef21-c257-414c-aae4-0e26b8f27cb5\">근육통뿐 아니라 척추 어깨 골반이 틀어져 있는 경우도 흔해서 추나 치료를 병행하는 친구들도 꽤 있죠. 부모님들이 걱정이 많은데, 치료받고 좋아지면 그만큼 만족도도 높아요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b5703ce0-419f-43c1-85ae-20e77a3f2062\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a885b17c-9c59-4611-994e-4cde9521a085\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-223ea647-07e1-4a5f-805c-d6b89734d785\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-223ea647-07e1-4a5f-805c-d6b89734d785\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/db51bc35381526ec.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1312\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/db51bc35381526ec.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/db51bc35381526ec.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"656\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-631da297-ef77-4daf-8ba4-daabaa74f90d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6a9e16ca-9ab4-44fc-b9be-3cdb4b96b80f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b6fe9f61-ffc9-47e8-bb15-d56b00989af6\">남성역 이수한의원의 나효석 원장님은 한의학 석사, 한방부인과 전문의입니다. 더구나 애 둘을 키우면서 함소아한의원에서 오랜 기간 소아진료를 했었던 분이라 어린이 소아청소년 진료를 잘 보십니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2d1c4b61-142e-491b-b2bd-6111058a700d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-2d1c4b61-142e-491b-b2bd-6111058a700d\", \"src\" : \"https://modo-phinf.pstatic.net/20221206_137/1670308959713gmrqn_PNG/mosauqlkvN.png?type=w720\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1080\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://modo-phinf.pstatic.net/20221206_137/1670308959713gmrqn_PNG/mosauqlkvN.png?type=w720\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cdc30f27-a53d-464f-b84e-e9c23e532636\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-662a0f63-b146-43da-9e8a-487efb21e03f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2ae620be-f0b5-4cea-af00-f827de36f74d\">특히 아이들의 키 성장 진료를 잘 하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e71d994e-063b-47ce-a04e-f00385b41f33\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8bc8c5bf-7a5d-4baf-881d-88a39f12e92c\">성장이 느려 키가 아주 작은 애들도 성장치료에 관심이 많지만, 요즘엔 평균 키는 되는데도 더 크고 싶어서 성장치료를 하는 아이들이 부쩍 늘었어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-04d13689-1838-4550-826d-bbe6556b3799\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c948c3e1-80ca-4570-a4f5-e428061d4b1c\">전에는 부모님이 자녀를 조금이라도 더 크게 하고 싶어서 자녀를 이수한의원에 데리고 왔었는데, 지금은 아이들 스스로가 더 크고 싶다고 하는 경우도 많더라고요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-13a85139-13b1-49ab-8825-49c04598c586\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-71bbd5b4-42f5-4d9a-a850-4238a7a8caf1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f81714db-6a26-4353-96f3-93da4a76cb26\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-657679ae-408d-4cbf-ba0e-7b66b95e71ee\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b7d82483-6ca8-4f98-8472-4f91fed4ee8e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ac3ee920-a5d3-447e-b398-8a745254bb8d\">돌이 되기 전 영유아들부터 어린이집, 유치원, 초등, 중등, 고등까지 소아 청소년들의 진료도 남성역 이수한의원에 내원하시면 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cd86cd92-558e-4882-8d7f-a928460c986b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-663bc102-9eb9-4a4b-98b8-c7cd2ecee11b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-tex